ray15reg">" We did a process flow analysis and found that an invoice was generally touched eight times by our staff. We had over a dozen staff doing data entry in accounts payable alone, our processes were 10 years behind the times.\r\n"</div>\r\n<!--<div  class="readbutton" align="right"><a href="customers.html" class="gray" >Read Case Study</a></div>-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="conlt12" style="display:none;">\r\n<div class="conlt">\r\n<img src="wp-content/themes/elap-cloud/images/tuintoms-logo.png" alt="alt"><br/>\r\n<div class="gray15"><strong>Kim Collins</strong><br/>\r\nExecutive Manager Finance\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class="conrt" >\r\n<div class="gray15reg">"We had a total of four AP staff employed full time just following up, manually inputting and checking invoices. In the last couple of days of every ?end of month?, our accounts staff would be incredibly busy processing as a significant number of invoices for the company would land on their desk in that last week."</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- <div  class="readbutton" align="right"><a href="customers.html" class="gray">Read Case Study</a></div>-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="conlt13" style="display:none;">\r\n<div class="conlt">\r\n<img src="wp-content/themes/elap-cloud/images/zespirelogo1.png" alt="alt"><br/>\r\n<div class="gray15"><strong>Gregg Liebenberg</strong><br/>\r\nSolutions Manager, Zespri International\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class="conrt" >\r\n<div class="gray15reg">"The Efficiency Leaders team across the board has come together to ensure we have a solution that is robust and delivers on the requirements, whilst minimising our cost, which is a fantastic outcome."\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- <div  class="readbutton" align="right"><a href="customers.html" class="gray">Read Case Study</a></div>-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="conlt14" style="display:none;">\r\n<div class="conlt">\r\n<img src="wp-content/themes/elap-cloud/images/corscoinactive.png" alt="alt"><br/>\r\n<div class="gray15"><strong>Dale Allen</strong><br/>\r\nCouncil''s Executive Manager-Finance,Coffs Harbour City Council\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class="conrt" >\r\n<div class="gray15reg">"We did a process flow analysis and found that an invoice was generally touched eight times by our staff. We had over a dozen staff doing data entry in accounts payable alone, our processes were 10 years behind the times.\r\n" </div>\r\n\r\n<!-- <div  class="readbutton" align="right"><a href="customers.html" class="gray">Read Case Study</a></div>-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="conlt15" style="display:none;">\r\n<div class="conlt">\r\n<img src="wp-content/themes/elap-cloud/images/urbanlogo.png" alt="alt"><br/>\r\n<div class="gray15"><strong></strong><br/>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class="conrt" >\r\n<div class="gray15reg">"The business is now well placed to manage the rapid expansion plans without increasing back office overheads. This would not have been possible without this technology.\r\n" </div>\r\n\r\n<!--     <div  class="readbutton" align="right"><a href="customers.html" class="gray">Read Case Study</a></div>-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="brandscroller1">\r\n<div  class="col5 remuera" > <a href="#" ></a></div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n\r\n<div id="conlt10">\r\n<div class="conlt">\r\n<img src="wp-content/themes/elap-cloud/images/remuicklogoact.png" alt="alt"><br/>\r\n<div class="gray15"><strong>Chris Davies</strong><br/>General Manager - Remuera Golf Club\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class="conrt" >\r\n<div class="gray15reg">" During the initial processes of integration and installation, the team at Efficiency Leaders went above and beyond what you would expect, with no query or task too large. The system has worked magic for our business and the result has been that we have now integrated ELAP Cloud throughout our entire business with integration between our Accounting package and POS software. The integration allows our current staff to spend more time running the business rather than just data entry.\r\n"</div>\r\n<!--<div  class="readbutton" align="right"><a href="customers.html" class="gray" >Read Case Study</a></div>-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div  class="graybox">\r\n<div class="featrin">\r\n<div id="gray11" class="content-contr" style="">\r\n<div align="center" class="gray301">ELAP Cloud Automation</div>\r\n<div class="featureinnerlf"><img id="slide7" src="wp-content/themes/elap-cloud/images/cloudautomation.jpg" alt="alt"></div>\r\n<div class="featureinnerrt">\r\n<div class="gray201">Most advanced technology for intelligent companies</div>\r\n<p>ELAP Cloud can process and store millions of invoices as well as the most important information of your company in just seconds, always in the most secure and protected way!</p>\r\n<p>\r\nUnlimited capacity and the most advanced technology on the market are the basis to ensure that our service is fast and safe.</p>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n<p class="buttondiv">\r\n<span class="greenbtn"><a href="signup.html">Get started now</a></span>\r\n<span class="greenbtn2"><a href="feature.html">View all features</a></span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="gray21" class="content-contr" style="display:none;">\r\n<div align="center" class="gray301">From paper to digital data in seconds</div>\r\n<div class="featureinnerlf"><img id="slide7" src="wp-content/themes/elap-cloud/images/paperimg.jpg" alt="alt"></div>\r\n<div class="featureinnerrt">\r\n<div class="gray201">No more manual data entry!</div>\r\n<p> Manual data entry is labour intensive and error prone and, let''s face it, not too many people enjoy it!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ELAP Cloud significantly reduces data entry and, importantly, it provides the data validation and integrity checks necessary to automate your Accounts Payable function.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Invoice information is automatically extracted, without the use of templates or barcodes etc., and then only accurate data will be sent to your business systems e.g. your finance and/or inventory system/s.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nSign up today and let ELAP Cloud Accounts Payable Automation take your stress and worry away!</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n<p class="buttondiv">\r\n<span class="greenbtn"><a href="signup.html">Get started now</a></span>\r\n<span class="greenbtn2"><a href="feature.html">View all features</a></span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="gray31" class="content-contr" style="display:none;">\r\n<div align="center" class="gray301">Line-to-Line Extraction and Verification</div>\r\n<div class="featureinnerlf"><img id="slide7" src="wp-content/themes/elap-cloud/images/linebyline.jpg" alt="alt"></div>\r\n<div class="featureinnerrt">\r\n<div class="gray201">Don''t miss any data</div>\r\n<p>Although most supplier invoices are different, ELAP Cloud collects all data line-by-line, recognizing the fields and storing the necessary information in their corresponding fields.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\nThe verification process allows you to review all documents thoroughly and make sure that everything is correct.</p>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n<p class="buttondiv" >\r\n<span class="greenbtn"><a href="signup.html">Get started now</a></span>\r\n<span class="greenbtn2"><a href="feature.html">View all features</a></span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="gray41" class="content-contr" style="display:none;">\r\n<div align="center" class="gray301">XERO Integration</div>\r\n<div class="featureinnerlf"><img id="slide7" src="wp-content/themes/elap-cloud/images/xero.jpg" alt="alt"></div>\r\n<div class="featureinnerrt">\r\n<div class="gray201">XERO and ELAP Cloud work together in perfect harmony</div>\r\n<p>The most advanced Accounts Payable Automation for Xero. ELAP Cloud improves the workflow of dealing with all your Accounts Payable invoices by in